Usage request<br/><br/>
<br/>
This command is used to get your mail when inside a post office. To erase<br/>
a letter which you have received, you must eat the letter.<br/>
<br/><br/><br/>
The request command also shows how much an item costs, but the shop keeper<br/>
may take into consideration other currencies than his default one.<br/>
<br/><br/>
